What I would do

Given:

CephCluster = HEALTH_OK

All ODF CSVs = Succeeded

No OBCs/ObjectBuckets exist

NooBaa DB recreated 6 days ago

Admin account missing from DB


I would proceed with recreating NooBaa metadata rather than spending time trying to repair the database manually.

One thing I'd like to see before you delete the NooBaa CR:

oc get cephobjectstore -n openshift-storage
oc get cephobjectstoreuser -n openshift-storage

That will confirm the RGW/object-store pieces are healthy and that only NooBaa metadata is broken.
